	(35,1,'2013-04-19 20:33:29','2013-04-19 20:33:29','<div class=\"products-container\"><header id=\"page-header\">\r\n<h1>Advanced Technologies</h1>\r\n</header>\r\n<div class=\"product\">\r\n\r\n<h2>Embedded LEDs</h2>\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://local.customglass/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/category_slug.jpg\" />Guardian’s patented process for embedding LEDs in laminated glass gives customers a myriad of styling options. Whether it’s prominently displaying a brand name in lights or replacing traditional exterior turn signals and brake lights, Guardian’s embedded LED solution takes sophistication and styling to a whole new level. \r\n\r\nCompanies no longer have to rely on decals that are susceptible to wear and tear from exposure to the elements. Instead, brand names, makes, models and more can be displayed in lights that are permanently protected by Guardian glass.\r\n\r\nGuardian’s embedded LEDs are also perfect for exterior indicators including turn signals, brake lights, flashers and more. We’ve even developed methods for diffusing the light from the LEDs, which creates applications for interior, ambient lighting.\r\n\r\nLEDs are available in multiple colors and circuits can be designed to run on multiple DC voltages to meet customer requirements.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"product\">\r\n\r\n<h2>Photovoltaic Roof Glass</h2>\r\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://local.customglass/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/category_slug.jpg\" />The concept is simple: collect energy from the sun and convert it to usable power for a vehicle. The execution however, is best left to the glass experts at Custom Glass Solutions.\r\n\r\nFrom the Toyota Prius to the Fisker Karma, photovoltaic (PV) roof glass is becoming more prevalent in the automotive industry. Guardian Custom Glass Solutions is taking similar technology and adapting it for use in vehicles with substantial real estate available for PV cells like recreational vehicles, heavy trucks, trains, buses, ships and more.\r\n\r\nGuardian’s PV roof glass solution utilizes low-iron, laminated glass to protect the PV cells from the elements and expose the cells to as much sunlight as possible. We are able to customize size, shape and artwork to seamlessly integrate PV roof glass into customer designs. Ask us how PV roof glass could power your application.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"product\">\r\n\r\n<h2>Switchable Glass</h2>\r\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://local.customglass/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/category_slug.jpg\" />Guardian’s Switchable Glass transitions from opaque to transparent with the flick of a switch. This high-tech privacy glass solution uses a low-voltage electrical current to arrange liquid crystal molecules into a pattern that makes glass transparent when turned on. Turned off, the liquid crystal molecules revert to a random pattern, diffusing the light and causing the glass to become opaque.\r\n\r\nCustom Glass Solutions is offering switchable glass in various applications for recreational vehicles, ships, limousines and more. \r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n</div>','Advanced Technologies','','publish','open','open','','advanced-technologies','','','2013-04-29 03:53:04','2013-04-29 03:53:04','',0,'http://local.customglass/?page_id=35',0,'page','',0),
